{"tid":2023920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【智將】本周將重開公眾游泳池及泳灘　徐英偉：限制人數不多於8人","createTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T08:56:24.000Z","uid":6497,"like":187,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"8f58c75fa3be593c84f0a87412d34694063796cf","tid":2023920,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200519/s00001/1589880008585/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200519%2Fs00001%2F1589880008585%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2Fz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=85ff3f5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200519%2Fs00001%2F1589880008585%2F&h=710f8e19\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200519/s00001/1589880008585/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200519/s00001/bb5d2df7d2ac27760fa77a8d8205321f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200519%2Fs00001%2Fbb5d2df7d2ac27760fa77a8d8205321f.jpg&h=6a6e072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200519/s00001/bb62b4790ebfac2a0c82d2e140b1addb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200519%2Fs00001%2Fbb62b4790ebfac2a0c82d2e140b1addb.jpg&h=d5bc1aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民政事務局長徐英偉今午（19日）於記者會表示，康文署將於周四（21日）重開更多康樂設施，包括30個公眾游泳池（當中只開放部分設施如主池及副池）、舞蹈室、健身室及運動攀登設施等；周六（23日）亦將開放15個泳灘，但會限制人數少於8人，並隔開淋浴間。<br />\n<br />\n徐英偉表示，「依家其實嗰個疫情，我必須再重新提一提係未完，所以例如我哋去到沙灘游水嘅時候，我哋就算開放返，我哋都希望保持住少過8人呢個要求」，但他未有進一步解釋如何執行限制少於8人的規定。徐英偉指出，部分設施政府仍未有信心開放，如兒童遊樂設施、較多肢體碰撞的球場等。"},{"pid":"bea31756342e199eaf668b0d9078325a3c6f22c9","tid":2023920,"uid":173179,"like":176,"dislike":0,"score":176,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:04:38.000Z","msg":"